"     <span class=\"medCalcFontOneBold\">",
"      Notes",
"     </span>",
"     <ul class=\"medCalcFontOne\">",
"      <li>",
"       0.8 g/mL is the specific gravity of ethanol and 0.6 is the volume of distribution of ethanol.",
