"       <b>",
"        Percent Ethanol",
"       </b>",
"       of beverages is",
"       <b>",
"        Proof",
"       </b>",
"       / 1.75",
"      </li>",
"      <li>",
"       For example, 80 proof vodka is 40 percent ethanol in the US, but is 46 percent ethanol in the UK or Australia.  Use the pull-down unit selector to choose the appropriate",
